Repost from @bridgetbragerhair
•
Restraint is a noble quality. Listening to your gut and your body, also noble. 

Anyone who sets the bar high for self perseverance is admirable. 
If we had more of that maybe people would be a little less insane? 
The thought that anyone owes anyone anything on a big or small stage is outrageous. 
Woman (men too) must be sure of this. Sticking up for yourself - advocating for yourself is 👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻
@simonebiles I ride with you. #yaw 🤠❤️
